api_list.description:
To generate a password, make a POST request with a json that looks as follows:

{
  "nbSmallLetters": "5",
  "nbCapitalLetters": "3",
  "nbChars": "7",
  "nbNumbers": "4",
  "allowedChars": "@#$%"
}

You will receive the password (pwd) in the body of the response:

{
  "statusCode": 200,
  "body": {
    "pwd": "f6$z$0Zy8@%M%L6zu%#"
  }
}
